args: What's up with Zace? Don't think the guy's\nblinked once since Elisanne started her\ndaily trainin'.
Nah, I don't buy that for a second.\nHe don't strike me as the type to be\ninterested in romance.
And I'm telling you, that's gotta be it!\nLook at him—can't you see the smoldering\ngaze of a man in love?
Hey, uh, Zace? Don't wanna pry or nothin'\nbut did ya just say ＂simply beautiful＂?
And were you talking about Elisanne?!
Ah, yes. She is quite beautiful.
Zace? In love? With Elisanne?\nMan, my mind is BLOWN over here.
You probably have a real tight feeling deep\nin your chest, right?!
I'm not certain I follow you, but I DO feel\nmoved to the core of my being.
Welp, that settles it. It's gotta be love!\nAnd that means you should go confess\nyour feelings to her RIGHT NOW!
Ain't no reason to hem and haw about it.\nI'm with Notte—just get over there and\nput it all out in the open.
Don't listen to this idiot, Zace! You can't\njust waltz over and open your big mouth;\nyou need to set the mood!
Nope! In a situation like this, yer best bet\nis to just get right to the point. ...Oh,\nhey there, {player_name}!
Looks like you're all excited about\nsomething. What's going on?
{player_name}, help us out here.\nAdvise Zace in the ways of love.
Surely you agree that you need a little\nstyle when you're talkin' to a lady, right?\nNot like this big idiot here!
Also, I'm not sure I'm much of an expert\nwhen it comes to love.
But if you love someone, it's probably best\nto just tell them so clearly and honestly.
Hmm. Yes, I suppose you're right.\n...Very well. I'll tell her how I feel.
I clearly and honestly told her what I think,\nand she accused me of ＂ghoulishness.＂
Yes, but it also doesn't really sound like\nElisanne to crush someone like that.
Actually, yeah. I guess not. What exactly\ndid you say to her, Zace?
As you advised honesty, I simply told her\nthat her bones were lovely.
Indeed. Elisanne's skeletal structure is\na thing of true beauty.
Her scapula and sacral vertebrae?\nThe flow from her shoulders to her back\nand then to her waist? Simply splendid.
Ah, and her radial styloid process? I never\ndreamed I'd lay eyes on a thing of such\nutter beauty!
Oh, that reminds me! Ranzal, you yourself\nhave gorgeous femurs.
And the delicate curve of Notte's coccyx\nis quite remarkable.
Wait, is that my BUTT?! How would you\neven know what that looks like, creeper?!
When one is an expert on bones,\nclothing is no hindrance.
WHAAAT?! Agh, stop looking at meee!
Ah! I feel such passion welling up inside\nme! Could this also be love?!
